they'd rather stay and take

00:23:55.040 --> 00:23:58.360
their chances, literally
abandon their property

00:23:58.360 --> 00:24:00.008
and live elsewhere.

00:24:03.002 --> 00:24:05.996
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:24:11.984 --> 00:24:14.479
