three channels, by the way.

00:32:10.120 --> 00:32:11.890
So there's other
channels that are active.

00:32:11.890 --> 00:32:15.550
I just wanted you to get
the cinematic scale, a feel,

00:32:15.550 --> 00:32:17.890
for the work.

00:32:17.890 --> 00:32:22.300
So in that scene--

00:32:22.300 --> 00:32:24.190
so once we move
into the theater,

00:32:24.190 --> 00:32:25.750
the free radicals
are all wearing

00:32:25.750 --> 00:32:29.620
